Class HederaContractID

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hedera.sdk.common.HederaContractID
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class HederaContractID
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The ID for a smart contract, it is composed of a shard number, a realm number and a contract number
